OL,3,CMum's mission to feed the families of
OL,4,Cchildren in hospital in daughter's
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,FOne of Sophie's dying wishes was that
OL,8,Fthe situation should change. And that
OL,9,Fhas led Charlotte to set up a charity
OL,10,Fthat now provides drinks, snacks,
OL,11,Ffrozen meals and other essentials for
OL,12,Fparents at 12 hospitals across the
OL,13,FSouth.
OL,15,FIt's called Sophie's Legacy and last
OL,16,Fyear it raised #450,000 and helped
OL,17,F60,000 families on children's wards at
OL,18,Fplaces like the Queen Alexandra
OL,19,FHospital in Portsmouth and Southampton
OL,20,FGeneral.
