OL,7,FNow, Charlotte's tireless work has
OL,8,Fearned her a nomination in ITV
OL,9,FMeridian's Pride of Britain Fundraiser
OL,10,Fof the Year award 2024.
OL,12,F"I'm really proud as a mum to be
OL,13,Frunning the charity in her (Sophie's)
OL,14,Fmemory, knowing that she actually
OL,15,Fwanted this.
