OL,7,F"There's never been a thought really
OL,8,Ffor the hospitals nationwide around
OL,9,Fthe parent that stays overnight with
OL,10,Ftheir child who has no access to any
OL,11,Fcooking facilities to feed them, "
OL,12,Fsaid Charlotte.
OL,14,F"Having access to a frozen meal or
OL,15,Fthings like that we provide is
OL,16,Fvirtually a lifeline for some of these
OL,17,Ffamilies who can't leave the ward."
