OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,FSophie's Legacy is also running a
OL,8,Fpilot project in 15 other hospitals up
OL,9,Fand down the country that helps with
OL,10,Ffeeding parents.
OL,12,F"We don't want this to be a postcode
OL,13,Flottery that depends on where you are,
OL,14,Fwhether you get fed. We want every
OL,15,Fhospital in the country to be feeding
OL,16,Fparents and that's my ultimate aim."
OL,18,FThrough Sophie's Legacy, Charlotte has
OL,19,Fcreated a whole system of support for
OL,20,Fparents with children in hospital.
